test_large_range:
assert [0, 1, 2] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 1, 2]
test_even_range:
assert [-2] == [-2, -4, -6]
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: -4
  Full diff:
  - [-2, -4, -6]
  + [-2]
test_positive_range:
assert [1, 2] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2]
